k\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:333:\"Let&#8217;s say your email content is already pretty strong. You&#8217;ve got good open rates, decent clickthroughs and a steady flow of traffic to your site and landing pages. What else could you really need? How about a bigger list, with more quality leads? Or a higher conversion rate for all of that traffic, including more [...]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Hunter Boyle\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2804:\"<p><img src=\"http://blog-cdn.aweber-static.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/thumb4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"thumb\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"img-right\" /></p>\n<p>Let&#8217;s say your email content is already pretty strong.</p>\n<p>You&#8217;ve got good open rates, decent clickthroughs and a steady flow of traffic to your site and landing pages.</p>\n<p>What else could you really need?</p>\n<p>How about a bigger list, with more quality leads? Or a higher conversion rate for all of that traffic, including more email sign-ups or ecommerce transactions &#8212; say, a 41% lift in increase per site visitor. A few ideas for new tests couldn&#8217;t hurt, either.</p>\n<p>Perfect timing: Our first guest webinar of 2013 will dive into all of those subjects.</p>\n<h2>Conversion Testing Demystified</h2>\n<p>We know email optimization testing can be intimidating, even for experienced marketers.</p>\n<p>That&#8217;s why we teamed up with the <a href=\"http://www.widerfunnel.com\">conversion experts at WiderFunnel</a>. If more effective testing is one of your top priorities, join me and Chris Goward, CEO of WiderFunnel for this special guest session.</p>\n<div style=\"background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #D9D9D9; margin: 15px auto; padding: 15px; border-radius: 7px; moz-border-radius: 7px; webkit-border-radius: 7px; font-size: 12px;  font-style: italic; line-height: 18px;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><a href=\"http://bit.ly/aweber-wf-webinar\">Optimizing Email: Tests &amp; Methods To Increase Conversions</a></span></p>\n<div style=\"float: right;\">\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/aweber-wf-webinar\"><img src=\"http://blog-cdn.aweber-static.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/cover61.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"cover6\" width=\"155\" height=\"200\" style=\"border: 4px solid #ffffff;-webkit-box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.75);<br />\n-moz-box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.75); box-shadow: 0 1px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.75); margin-left: 15px;\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p>In this free live webinar, we will:</p>\n<ul style=\"padding: 0px;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 10px 25px; line-height: 18px;\">Reveal keys to tests that achieved double-digit gains</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 10px 25px; line-height: 18px;\">Squash common myths about optimization, and</li>\n<li style=\"margin: 10px 25px; line-height: 18px;\">Help you put a testing framework in place that gets results.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We&#8217;ll discuss your specific challenges in a live Q&amp;A session. Plus, you&#8217;ll also get an awesome checklist &#8212; <strong>31 Ways to Optimize Conversions</strong> &#8212; free when you sign up.</p>\n<p><strong>Date:</strong> Wednesday, February 27, 2013<br />\n<strong>Time:</strong> 1:00 pm ET / 10:00 am PT</p>\n<p>Space is limited and seats are filling up, so <a href=\"http://bit.ly/aweber-wf-webinar\">reserve your spot now</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a